    <div class="exp-desc">
        <p>
            After being working for a tiny startup for almost three years I wanted to try some kind of bigger company and continue working with Elixir. That's why I decided to join Derivco which is the company that with more that 4.000 workers around the world is Software provider for Betway, one of the bigger sportbook around the world.
        </p>
        <p>
            At Derivco I was part of the Core team in charge of develop and mantain serveral service in Ruby, Elixir and Golang.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>
